This repository contains original research code, experimental workflows,
and implementation details related to the BFSET (Beard Face Set) dataset,
developed by Cognisoft.

The BFSET dataset, its name, structure, images, annotations, metadata,
processing scripts, and any associated intellectual property are the exclusive
property of Cognisoft. The dataset itself is NOT distributed through this
repository and may not be accessed, used, copied, or redistributed without
explicit written authorization from Cognisoft.

No part of this repository — including source code, notebooks, algorithms,
figures, experimental designs, or derivative work — may be reproduced, copied,
modified, distributed, or used in any form or by any means without prior
written permission from Cognisoft.

